133
00:10:34,140 --> 00:10:34,730
Huh?

134
00:10:35,100 --> 00:10:35,820
Co?

135
00:10:56,990 --> 00:10:59,170
Vrátil jsem se,

136
00:10:59,850 --> 00:11:01,530
